{% doc %}
  @prompt
    A T-shirt, a hoodie mockup design is required. One category should contain 1 to 10 sample images in color.
    All sample images should be uploaded.
    
    In it,
    
    When choosing a T-shirt - two options should be given as adults, children, then
    01) Adults - 2 options for men or women
    02) Children - 2 options for women or men
    
    Or
    When choosing a hoodie - two options should be given as adults, children, adults, children, then
    01) Adults - 2 options for men or women
    02) Children - 2 options for women or men
    
    Customer needs an option to upload 4 designs. They should be separate, with transform controls to change size, position and rotation in the preview area.
    
    Send me an email and get the parts, customer details., A T-shirt, a hoodie mockup design is required. One category should contain 1 to 10 sample images in color.
    All sample images should be uploaded.
    
    In it,
    
    When choosing a T-shirt - two options should be given as adults, children, then
    01) Adults - 2 options for men or women
    02) Children - 2 options for women or men
    
    Or
    When choosing a hoodie - two options should be given as adults, children, adults, children, then
    01) Adults - 2 options for men or women
    02) Children - 2 options for women or men
    
    Customer needs an option to upload 4 designs. They should be separate, with transform controls to change size, position and rotation in the preview area.
    
    Send me an email and get the parts, customer details., Create a mockup editor for T-shirts, Hoodies. Adult man sample image 10 woman sample image 10. Child boy sample image 10 girl sample image 10 Content should be included
    All sample images should be able to be uploaded.
    
    There
    
    When choosing T-shirts - Two options should be given as adults, children then
    01) Adults - 2 options as men or women
    02) Children - 2 options as women or men
    
    Or
    When choosing Hoodies - Two options should be given as adults, children then
